OL,3,CTeen who spent four months in hospital
OL,4,Cafter stoma bag can start police career
OL,6,FA teenager who spent four months in
OL,7,Fhospital after having a stoma bag
OL,8,Ffitted is celebrating the start of her
OL,9,Fcareer in the police after picking up
OL,10,Fher A-level results.
OL,12,FTeigan Griffiths, 19, thought her
OL,13,Fdreams of becoming a policewoman were
OL,14,Fover when, just one year into her A-
OL,15,Flevels, she needed emergency surgery
OL,16,Fafter becoming rapidly ill.
OL,18,FThe then 17-year-old needed a stoma
OL,19,Fbag permanently fitted and then spent
OL,20,Ffour months in hospital due to a
OL,21,Fsubsequent sepsis diagnosis.
