OL,3,CTeen who spent four months in hospital
OL,4,Cafter stoma bag can start police career
OL,6,FBut, on Thursday morning, she was
OL,7,Fcelebrating at Coleg y Cymoedd after
OL,8,Fgetting an A* and two As in her
OL,9,Fcriminology, psychology and sociology
OL,10,FA-levels - and being able to start a
OL,11,Fthree-year apprenticeship with South
OL,12,FWales Police.
OL,14,F"After my operation, I thought I could
OL,15,Feither mope around or be positive and
OL,16,Fstill follow my dreams," Teigan, from
OL,17,FGilfach Goch in Rhondda Cynon Taf,
OL,18,Fsaid.
