OL,3,CTeen who spent four months in hospital
OL,4,Cafter stoma bag can start police career
OL,6,F"I contacted South Wales Police to
OL,7,Ftell them about my situation and they
OL,8,Fsaid it wasn't a problem and that they
OL,9,Fwould even create a specialist uniform
OL,10,Ffor me that is reinforced to protect
OL,11,Fmy stoma bag.
OL,13,F"I'm so thankful to my amazing college
OL,14,Ftutors for their support ` I wouldn't
OL,15,Fhave come back to college without
OL,16,Ftheir help and encouragement."
OL,18,F"I've wanted to join the police for a
OL,19,Fwhile and was so upset when I thought
OL,20,Fthat my operation would me that career
OL,21,Fwasn't possible," she added.
