OL,3,CTeen who spent four months in hospital
OL,4,Cafter stoma bag can start police career
OL,6,F"The reality is that my stoma bag
OL,7,Fhasn't stopped me from doing anything.
OL,8,FI really thought it would impact my
OL,9,Flife at the time but it hasn't ` I've
OL,10,Fjust had to adjust to things slightly."
OL,12,FTeigan also wants to raise awareness
OL,13,Fabout stoma bags and tackle the stigma
OL,14,Faround them.
OL,16,F"Having my stoma fitted has been the
OL,17,Fbest decision ` it has taken away all
OL,18,Fthe pain," she said.
