OL,3,CTeen who spent four months in hospital
OL,4,Cafter stoma bag can start police career
OL,6,F"I'm open about it and want more
OL,7,Fpeople to know about them. There's a
OL,8,Fstigma that you can't do much once you
OL,9,Fhave one.
OL,11,F"I had a fear I would lose everything
OL,12,Fand have a different life but that's
OL,13,Fnot the case ` I want other people in
OL,14,Fthat situation to know that and not
OL,15,Flose hope for the future. I'd like to
OL,16,Fwrite a book about my experience one
OL,17,Fday."
